window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My life was nothing but mundane until the night I met her. </b></p> <p>Lustful, beautiful...and also a <i>fairy.</i></p> <p>And after one wild night, she's chosen me as the savior of an entire race of fae—a race that has lost the means to protect themselves, to rebuild everything they’ve lost, and most of all, to procreate.&nbsp;</p> <p>They need to be rebuilt and re-bred, and I’m just the man for the job.</p>"; 
